title: Start
---
// Set the stage before anyone talks (loads sprites invisibly)
<<set_left Ren>>
<<set_right Akane>>

// Trigger the entrance animations to slide them on screen
<<enter_left>>
<<enter_right>>

// Highlight Ren, darken Akane
<<highlight left>>
Ren: Yo.

// Highlight Akane, darken Ren
<<highlight right>>
Akane: Yo yo.
Akane: So, what do you want to test next?

// The Options Menu will appear here!
-> Ren: Let's test the 3D Hub interaction.
    <<highlight left>>
    Ren: I want to walk around and trigger this conversation manually.
    <<highlight right>>
    Akane: Sounds like a plan. We'll need a raycast for that.
-> Ren: Let's test the mini-game transitions.
    <<highlight left>>
    Ren: I want to see if we can load a hacking level straight from this dialogue.
    <<highlight right>>
    Akane: Ooh, jumping straight into the 2D action. I like it!
-> Ren: Say nothing.
    <<highlight left>>
    Ren: ...
    <<highlight right>>
    Akane: Silent treatment? Really?

// The branches merge back together here
// Akane exits the scene
<<exit_right>>

// Highlight Ren again
<<highlight left>>
Ren: Wait, where did you go? We haven't even started!
===